<div class="modal fade" id="importModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" data-bs-backdrop="static">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content bg-dark text-white border-0 shadow-lg" style="border-radius: 20px;">
            <div class="modal-header border-0 pb-0">
                <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-excel-fill text-success me-2"></i> Upload Sps</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <form asp-action="ImportExcel" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="importForm">
                <div class="modal-body p-4">
                    <!-- Panduan Upload Sps -->
                    <div class="card bg-gradient mb-3 border-0 shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h6 class="text-white fw-bold mb-3">
                                <i class="bi bi-upload me-2"></i>Cara Upload Sps:
                            </h6>
                            <ol class="text-white mb-2" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                                <li>Download <strong>Template Sps</strong> di bawah</li>
                                <li>Isi kolom sesuai data — kolom MIN/STD/MAX bisa diisi manual</li>
                                <li>Kolom <strong>Item List</strong> di ujung kanan bersifat <em>opsional</em> (bisa upload terpisah)</li>
                                <li>Upload file Excel (.xlsx)</li>
                            </ol>
                            <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-3 p-2" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">
                                <strong class="text-warning d-block mb-1">
                                    <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>Kolom Wajib:
                                </strong>
                                <ul class="mb-0 text-white" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">
                                    <li><strong>ID Excel</strong> (Kolom A)</li>
                                    <li><strong>Machine</strong> (Kolom C)</li>
                                    <li><strong>NO. DOC</strong> (Kolom D)</li>
                                </ul>
                                <hr class="border-white border-opacity-25 my-2">
                                <span class="text-white-50"><i class="bi bi-lightbulb me-1"></i>Kolom ± (toleransi): isi format <strong class="text-warning">X±Y</strong> — sistem hitung MIN &amp; MAX otomatis. Nilai manual di kolom MIN/STD/MAX tetap disimpan sebagai pembanding.</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="alert alert-info mb-3 py-2" role="alert" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                            <div>
                                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-spreadsheet me-1"></i>
                                <strong>Belum punya template?</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                                <a asp-action="DownloadTemplateFull" class="btn btn-success btn-sm fw-bold shadow-sm">
                                    <i class="bi bi-download me-1"></i> Template Sps
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <small class="text-muted d-block mt-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
                            <strong>Template Sps</strong> memuat seluruh kolom database lengkap dengan kolom <strong class="text-warning">MIN / STD / MAX</strong> terpisah untuk setiap parameter. Kolom <strong class="text-success">Item List</strong> opsional.
                        </small>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="upload-area border border-secondary border-dashed p-4 text-center rounded-3 bg-black bg-opacity-25 position-relative">
                         <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up fs-1 text-info mb-2 d-block"></i>
